    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Kashu Clan, Level 8+</p><p>Your genjutsu's sound is completely overwhelming and has the ability to creep into the very soul of any living being. You gain the following benefits</p><p>• All Kashu Clan Hijutsu that impose a rank of Disorientation now impose an additional rank</p><p>• A creature with 0 chakra points gains disadvantage on saving throws from jutsu with the auditory keyword and cannot gain advantage by any means</p><p>• Kashu Clan Hijutsu, that don't already reduce chakra, reduce an opponent's chakra by half the amount of damage dealt.</p>",
